{"tid":544251,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"你有一個隱定對象，然後你鐘意左第二個","createTime":"2018-01-29T10:33:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-29T11:58:32.000Z","uid":77895,"like":23,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"93d7176c8e83a9cb7a8c72462499e1d5e0ba0a9f","tid":544251,"uid":77895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T10:33:48.000Z","msg":"連登仔成日屌鳩人出軌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁我又黎問下<br />\n假設你已有隱定伴侶，未結婚，提都未提過<br />\n有一日，你發現自己鐘意左第二個<br />\n對方外形、學識等條件都好過你身邊嗰個，亦係你鐘意嘅類型<br />\n你地仲要十分投契，興趣等嘅野都好夾<br />\n你會唔會放棄你身邊嗰個同人地一齊？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 會<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔會<br />\n<br />\n唔好講咩我淨係愛我另一半，依家嘅情況係你已經變左心。你會留低？定跟隨自己嘅心意？<br />\n巴打絲打都歡迎投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcfae2ea4a8cd828a1aa8b8bf758e1aae5175f69","tid":544251,"uid":67238,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T10:36:21.000Z","msg":"有冇鐘意右？肥絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3b4b46e18b18271e1f812136c2abeb98463c786","tid":544251,"uid":123922,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T10:37:09.000Z","msg":"乜撚野係隱定呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edc813421a260b38afb902c221760bce63105ed3","tid":544251,"uid":134897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T10:37:35.000Z","msg":"隱定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e327fd66e739d6383fb7e45f8fbd0be22848acb","tid":544251,"uid":149487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T10:38:04.000Z","msg":"隱形<br />\n穩定<br />\n你想打邊個？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"506e680ba9b6000e5aaeec55ab3bb80a905dc846","tid":544251,"uid":77895,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-